{"tid":2108533,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"食衞局將檢測40萬高風險者　不涉提供個人資料到境外","createTime":"2020-07-14T15:10:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T01:09:13.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"beae40fc6e7ac01be88e1fe2df6125dba7aeab1a","tid":2108533,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:10:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537749-20200714.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537749-20200714.htm&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuByAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=def1f5b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537749-20200714.htm&h=d75a5b91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537749-20200714.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局表示，當局獲悉市場上只有3間私營化驗所，能在短時間內提供數以萬計規模的核酸檢測服務，政府決定透過防疫抗疫基金，以直接採購服務方式，向其中兩間化驗所「華昇診斷中心」及「Prenetics」採購檢測服務，為安老院舍、殘疾人士院舍及護養院員工、的士司機和食肆員工進行自願新型肺炎病毒檢測，初步估計涉及約40萬人。<br />\n<br />\n食衞局說，檢測本星期開始分批進行，首先檢測安老院舍、殘疾人士院舍及護養院員工，以及的士司機兩個較高風險群組。由於不同界別的檢測安排有所不同，成本亦不同。當局仍在與個別公司商討相關檢測服務費用，會確保採購費用合理，稍後公布資料，又表示檢測工作流程，並不涉及將任何個人資料提供予境外機構或人士。<br />\n<br />\n食衞局說，香港物業管理公司協會亦與另一間化驗所「中國檢驗有限公司」商討，為物業管理界別提供檢測服務，政府防疫抗疫基金會提供資助。<br />\n<br />\n另外，衞生署早前向 5間本地私營化驗所直接採購檢測服務，相關私營化驗所今天開始協助進行檢測，每日合共可處理約1000個樣本。醫管局正探討在普通科門診診所設立特別櫃台，提供深喉唾液樣本瓶予懷疑有輕微病徵的病人，並希望接受病毒檢測的市民。"},{"pid":"adf3516e411380c10871f260e458d6bc6b85b332","tid":2108533,"uid":263197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:11:34.000Z","msg":"林鄭假抗疫、真賣港"},{"pid":"8db33d793da0002e80db429e534f5ceee093d1bc","tid":2108533,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adf3516e411380c10871f260e458d6bc6b85b332","tid":2108533,"uid":263197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:11:34.000Z","msg":"林鄭假抗疫、真賣港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a869647c6b3804451395715e7257f113463752","tid":2108533,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9cbd9bd5bd232120b307c86f68a075f59f50049","tid":2108533,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c11663e9e8443236a7c0b9ddc51d7e6d717f58","tid":2108533,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:50:23.000Z","msg":"喺國安法之下支那唔算境外"},{"pid":"0835dc6cfc4c90b9874cc1ebef9c8ae170e89cd4","tid":2108533,"uid":137078,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:52:56.000Z","msg":"訓咗半年<br />\n抗疫？<br />\n整口罩搵自己友<br />\n化驗益支那廠<br />\n半年時間<br />\n本地大把lab扮搵唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最L大問題係驗完唔知準定唔準"},{"pid":"d95d154d467dbe718abc2af43b2d68a03d42d155","tid":2108533,"uid":214502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:54:03.000Z","msg":"家陣驗呢D人已經太遲 已經到左社區爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d42c06196383ba31627e8c534514f0a1b0932e","tid":2108533,"uid":271545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:00:11.000Z","msg":"食物及衞生局：你怎麼這樣憑空汚人清白。香港人的個人資料能算個人資料麼？"},{"pid":"4b6f819f2a14ca01a2349a815b5c43b4b6ec2769","tid":2108533,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:29:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/武漢肺炎-為-40-萬人檢測病毒-政府直接採購無招標-涉款數以億元計/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%82%BA-40-%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E6%8E%A1%E8%B3%BC%E7%84%A1%E6%8B%9B%E6%A8%99-%E6%B6%89%E6%AC%BE%E6%95%B8%E4%BB%A5%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E8%A8%88%2F&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuByAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=f88399b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%82%BA-40-%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E6%8E%A1%E8%B3%BC%E7%84%A1%E6%8B%9B%E6%A8%99-%E6%B6%89%E6%AC%BE%E6%95%B8%E4%BB%A5%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E8%A8%88%2F&h=9c648c66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/武漢肺炎-為-40-萬人檢測病毒-政府直接採購無招標-涉款數以億元計/</a><br />\n 立場<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料顯示，北京華大基因研究中心（華大基因） 2010 年在香港成立「華大基因香港研發中心有限公司」，總部設於大埔工業邨。Prenetics 則是 2014 年由城市大學參與創立，2017年阿里巴巴創業者基金投資入股，保誠保險亦是股東之一。<br />\n<br />\n另外，林鄭月娥今日到慈雲山一所護養院，聽取「華大基因開設的華昇診斷中心」負責人講解，為院舍約八十名員工採集咽拭子樣本進行病毒檢測的安排及程序。她表示，政府會為四類較高風險群組進行病毒檢測，包括安老院舍、殘疾院舍及護養院員工、食肆員工、的士司機以及物業管理人員，以加強在社區的檢測，找出隱性患者，做到「早發現、早隔離、早治療」，減少病毒在社區傳播的風險。"},{"pid":"f190ab0203af80473076fa65f8fb8463c85ab89e","tid":2108533,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2a869647c6b3804451395715e7257f113463752","tid":2108533,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26581cfd269cb52a6bcc1e08621d99f32375c4c","tid":2108533,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9cbd9bd5bd232120b307c86f68a075f59f50049","tid":2108533,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:31:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1fcaaacfd951f022613fbc8c85ec4f278b5aaf7","tid":2108533,"uid":11663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:32:08.000Z","msg":"地球人的DNA是中國的，不涉及個人資料"},{"pid":"d6a4f12316ebdf5d0c5035988964f5b070ff4bca","tid":2108533,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f190ab0203af80473076fa65f8fb8463c85ab89e","tid":2108533,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2a869647c6b3804451395715e7257f113463752","tid":2108533,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:16:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9c64f3434ed49203878700446b75462bcb18ae","tid":2108533,"uid":160373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:35:31.000Z","msg":"信你老尾呀<br />\n而家港共講所有嘢, 調返轉嚟諗就無錯"},{"pid":"de6c683bc1010f76143c8ce988d98d7594cbdee5","tid":2108533,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4684c4276ae2c58dfc91c8e88658edabd043205","tid":2108533,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b6f819f2a14ca01a2349a815b5c43b4b6ec2769","tid":2108533,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:29:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/武漢肺炎-為-40-萬人檢測病毒-政府直接採購無招標-涉款數以億元計/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%82%BA-40-%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E6%8E%A1%E8%B3%BC%E7%84%A1%E6%8B%9B%E6%A8%99-%E6%B6%89%E6%AC%BE%E6%95%B8%E4%BB%A5%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E8%A8%88%2F&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuByAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=f88399b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%82%BA-40-%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E6%8E%A1%E8%B3%BC%E7%84%A1%E6%8B%9B%E6%A8%99-%E6%B6%89%E6%AC%BE%E6%95%B8%E4%BB%A5%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E8%A8%88%2F&h=9c648c66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/武漢肺炎-為-40-萬人檢測病毒-政府直接採購無招標-涉款數以億元計/</a><br />\n 立場<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料顯示，北京華大基因研究中心（華大基因） 2010 年在香港成立「華大基因香港研發中心有限公司」，總部設於大埔工業邨。Prenetics 則是 2014 年由城市大學參與創立，2017年阿里巴巴創業者基金投資入股，保誠保險亦是股東之一。<br />\n<br />\n另外，林鄭月娥今日到慈雲山一所護養院，聽取「華大基因開設的華昇診斷中心」負責人講解，為院舍約八十名員工採集咽拭子樣本進行病毒檢測的安排及程序。她表示，政府會為四類較高風險群組進行病毒檢測，包括安老院舍、殘疾院舍及護養院員工、食肆員工、的士司機以及物業管理人員，以加強在社區的檢測，找出隱性患者，做到「早發現、早隔離、早治療」，減少病毒在社區傳播的風險。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:36:29.000Z","msg":"華大基因（深交所：300676），原名北京華大基因研究中心，是中國的一家基因組測序（英語：Whole genome sequencing）中心[1]。該機構成立於1999年，先後完成了國際人類基因組計劃[2]「中國部分」（1%，承擔其中絕大部分工作）、國際人類基因組單體型圖計劃（10%）、第一個亞洲人基因組圖譜（「炎黃一號」）[3]、水稻基因組計劃、大熊貓基因組計劃[4]等多項具有國際先進水平的基因組研究工作。其於2017年登陸深交所創業板，短暫上揚後，公司市值在7個月內蒸發680億[5]，其後因信息披露違規數度接獲深交所問詢；至2019年5月，其市值較其高峰期跌去近七成[6]。<br />\n<br />\nFrom wiki"},{"pid":"1d8dc53b0d6c25e0ae6861337ed932d356c8b28e","tid":2108533,"uid":175402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:36:53.000Z","msg":"其實驗完仲高風險<br />\n隨時之後被捐內臟"},{"pid":"26af3adb8f8aeec6279103692e8dfc979e845105","tid":2108533,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7c11663e9e8443236a7c0b9ddc51d7e6d717f58","tid":2108533,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:50:23.000Z","msg":"喺國安法之下支那唔算境外"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:36:58.000Z","msg":"之前唔係話用咗一億將啲資料送晒中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f94b0708ff4c8c2d8edfd2f282c391ed5b0dbaa","tid":2108533,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\